    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a 2018 BMW 540i xDrive that perfectly balances performance and executive comfort. The Alpine White exterior remains vibrant and glossy, having been garage-kept for the majority of its life. While the body is straight and free of major dents, there are a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small, professionally touched-up scratch on the rear bumper. Inside, the Mocha Dakota leather is in wonderful shape, showing only light bolster wear on the driver's seat and no cracks or fading. All interior technology\u2014including the heads-up display, heated seats, and navigation\u2014is fully operational. Mechanically, the car is excellent; it has been serviced exclusively at BMW intervals, with a fresh oil change and a new set of Continental all-season tires installed just 2,000 miles ago. The 3.0L turbocharged engine pulls smoothly, and the transmission shifts are crisp. There is a slight bit of curb rash on the passenger-side front rim, but it does not affect the balance or drive quality. This is a reliable, well-documented luxury sedan ready for the road.",
